{"type":"message","id":"895a4e5d","parentId":"2d8b2cb6","timestamp":"2026-04-03T01:32:03.874Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_QyxyUqIedKHk0MfNw53wArMA","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Smart money / whale / KOL signal tracking\n\nUsage: onchainos signal [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>\n\nCommands:\n  chains  Get supported chains for market signals\n  list    Get latest signal list (smart money / KOL / whale activity)\n  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)\n\nOptions:\n      --base-url <BASE_URL>  Backend service URL (overrides config)\n      --chain <CHAIN>        Chain: ethereum, solana, base, bsc, polygon, arbitrum, sui, etc\n  -h, --help                 Print help\n\n---\nToken information\n\nUsage: onchainos token [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>\n\nCommands:\n  search                    Search for tokens by name, symbol, or address\n  info                      Get token basic info (name, symbol, decimals, logo)\n  holders                   Get token holder distribution (top 100)\n  trending                  Get trending / top tokens\n  price-info                Get detailed price info (price, market cap, liquidity, volume, 24h change)\n  liquidity                 Get top 5 liquidity pools for a token\n  hot-tokens                Get hot token list ranked by trending score or X mentions (max 100 results)\n  advanced-info             Get advanced token info (risk, creator, dev stats, holder concentration)\n  top-trader                Get top traders (profit addresses) for a token\n  trades                    Get token trade history on DEX, with optional tag and wallet filters\n  cluster-overview          Get token holder cluster concentration overview (cluster level, rug pull %, new address %)\n  cluster-top-holders       Get top 10/50/100 holder overview (holding %, trend, avg PnL, avg cost, avg sell)\n  cluster-list              Get holder cluster list (clusters of top 300 holders with address details)\n  cluster-supported-chains  Get supported chains for holder cluster analysis\n  help                      Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)\n\nOptions:\n      --base-url <BASE_URL>  Backend service URL (overrides config)\n      --chain <CHAIN>        Chain: ethereum, solana, base, bsc, polygon, arbitrum, sui, etc\n  -h, --help                 Print help"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":175,"aggregated":"Smart money / whale / KOL signal tracking\n\nUsage: onchainos signal [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>\n\nCommands:\n  chains  Get supported chains for market signals\n  list    Get latest signal list (smart money / KOL / whale activity)\n  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)\n\nOptions:\n      --base-url <BASE_URL>  Backend service URL (overrides config)\n      --chain <CHAIN>        Chain: ethereum, solana, base, bsc, polygon, arbitrum, sui, etc\n  -h, --help                 Print help\n\n---\nToken information\n\nUsage: onchainos token [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>\n\nCommands:\n  search                    Search for tokens by name, symbol, or address\n  info                      Get token basic info (name, symbol, decimals, logo)\n  holders                   Get token holder distribution (top 100)\n  trending                  Get trending / top tokens\n  price-info                Get detailed price info (price, market cap, liquidity, volume, 24h change)\n  liquidity                 Get top 5 liquidity pools for a token\n  hot-tokens                Get hot token list ranked by trending score or X mentions (max 100 results)\n  advanced-info             Get advanced token info (risk, creator, dev stats, holder concentration)\n  top-trader                Get top traders (profit addresses) for a token\n  trades                    Get token trade history on DEX, with optional tag and wallet filters\n  cluster-overview          Get token holder cluster concentration overview (cluster level, rug pull %, new address %)\n  cluster-top-holders       Get top 10/50/100 holder overview (holding %, trend, avg PnL, avg cost, avg sell)\n  cluster-list              Get holder cluster list (clusters of top 300 holders with address details)\n  cluster-supported-chains  Get supported chains for holder cluster analysis\n  help                      Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)\n\nOptions:\n      --base-url <BASE_URL>  Backend service URL (overrides config)\n      --chain <CHAIN>        Chain: ethereum, solana, base, bsc, polygon, arbitrum, sui, etc\n  -h, --help                 Print help","cwd":"/home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775179923871}}
